OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson's wife told
OL,7,Fpolice she was met with a "blank wall"
OL,8,Fwhen she repeatedly asked him about an
OL,9,Fincident where he had been alone in a
OL,10,Froom with an alleged victim of sexual
OL,11,Fabuse.
OL,13,FLady Eleanor Donaldson said what had
OL,14,Fhappened had made her feel
OL,15,F"uncomfortable" but insisted she had
OL,16,Fnever witnessed or known about any
OL,17,Finappropriate behaviour.
