OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FThe jury of seven men and five women
OL,7,Fat Newry Crown Court have been hearing
OL,8,Ffurther police interviews with the
OL,9,FDonaldsons following their arrest in
OL,10,FMarch 2024 over alleged historical
OL,11,Fsexual offences.
OL,13,FFormer DUP leader Jeffrey Donaldson,
OL,14,F63, has pleaded not guilty to 18
OL,15,Falleged offences.
OL,17,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,18,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,19,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,20,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008 involving
OL,21,Ftwo alleged victims.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
