OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1781035559
OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FComplainant A and B have both
OL,7,Fpreviously given evidence at the
OL,8,Ftrial. Both women allege they were
OL,9,Fabused as children.
OL,11,FEleanor Donaldson, 60, denies several
OL,12,Fcharges of aiding and abetting her
OL,13,Fhusband's alleged offending.
OL,15,FShe is facing a trial of the facts and
OL,16,Fis not participating in the
OL,17,Fproceedings.
OL,19,FDonaldson sat in the dock at the back
OL,20,Fof the court while the recordings were
OL,21,Fplayed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
