OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FIn her first interview with police,
OL,7,FEleanor Donaldson was asked if she was
OL,8,Fguilty of the offences for which she
OL,9,Fhad been arrested. She replied no.
OL,11,FShe then told police about an incident
OL,12,Fwhere she had gone to find her husband
OL,13,Fand he was in a room with Complainant
OL,14,FB, who was a teenager at the time.
OL,16,FThe court has previously heard B
OL,17,Fallege that the former MP had lifted
OL,18,Fher top and touched her breasts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
