OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FEleanor Donaldson said: "I just sort
OL,7,Fof remember just looking at him and
OL,8,Fsaying what are you doing."
OL,10,FShe said when she asked her husband
OL,11,Fabout it, he said it "was nothing" and
OL,12,Fthat he was "just talking".
OL,14,FShe added: "In the years that came
OL,15,Fafter that I never had any cause for
OL,16,Fconcern ever, I never felt that apart
OL,17,Ffrom thinking that that was strange
OL,18,Fand what was that about and I asked
OL,19,FJeffrey about it and he just dismissed
OL,20,Fit.
OL,26,@nD@YOUpD@[O]sD@VOUsD@bO]tD@MOUtD@ZO]vD@
OL,26,ALOU
