OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,F"I never had any other feeling that
OL,7,Fanything was wrong."
OL,9,FShe said: "I asked Jeffrey many times
OL,10,Fbut he had never given me a reason for
OL,11,Fwhy he was there or what he was doing.
OL,13,F"I asked him many times and it never
OL,14,Fcame to anything and he never gave me
OL,15,Fany answers."
OL,17,FWhen asked by the detective, if she
OL,18,Fhad a "clear view" of what had
OL,19,Fhappened, she said: "I could just see
OL,20,Fthat there were both standing there,
OL,21,Fbut that was it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@TO]qD@KOUuD@AOUwD@MO]zD@GOUzD@
