OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FThe detective asked her if she
OL,7,Fbelieved "something more" had been
OL,8,Fgoing on.
OL,10,FShe said: "Yes, because I was
OL,11,Funcomfortable. I was uncomfortable."
OL,13,FShe added: "Every time I did ask I was
OL,14,Fmet with a blank wall, it was not
OL,15,Fcoming out.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@YO]rD@KOUsD@dO]uD@LOU
