OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,F"I just lived to the best of my
OL,7,Fability and then other times it would
OL,8,Fstart eating at me again because I
OL,9,Fjust wanted to get to the bottom of it
OL,10,Fand even though all those years had
OL,11,Fpassed still to the back of my mind
OL,12,Fbecause that's the type of person I
OL,13,Fam."
OL,15,FThe detective asked if she had ever
OL,16,Fwitnessed any inappropriate behaviour
OL,17,Fbetween her husband and Complainant B.
OL,19,FShe said: "No, absolutely nothing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@DO]{D@KOU{D@cO]
