OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FThe court previously heard that when
OL,7,FComplainant B was a teenager she had
OL,8,Fvisited the Christian Family Centre in
OL,9,FArmoy where she met with Jeffrey
OL,10,FDonaldson.
OL,12,FReferring to this meeting, Eleanor
OL,13,FDonaldson said: "I didn't know this at
OL,14,Fthe time and I didn't know it until
OL,15,Fmany years had passed and in the
OL,16,Fcourse of conversation with him again,
OL,17,Fhe said... the questions that you're
OL,18,Fasking me, that has been dealt with."
OL,26,@uD@QOUzD@eO]
