OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FShe said her husband told her he had
OL,7,F"asked for forgiveness", it was
OL,8,Fgranted and "that was sorted".
OL,10,FShe said: "But I never knew what that
OL,11,Fwas because he wouldn't talk to me
OL,12,Fabout it."
OL,14,FAsked about the circumstances of an
OL,15,Falleged incident where Complainant B
OL,16,Fclaims she was raped by Jeffrey
OL,17,FDonaldson, Eleanor Donaldson said: "I
OL,18,Fwould say that didn't happen.
OL,19,FAbsolutely not, oh my goodness."
