OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FShe told police she was "devastated"
OL,7,Fhearing about the allegation.
OL,9,FShe added: "That's totally outside my
OL,10,Fknowledge of what I would expect from
OL,11,Fhim."
OL,13,FEleanor Donaldson also told police she
OL,14,Fhad no awareness of allegations made
OL,15,Fby Complainant A that she was sexually
OL,16,Fabused when she was a child.
OL,18,FShe said: "I've never been party or
OL,19,Fseen anything like that."
