OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FAsked if she was aware of occasions
OL,7,Fwhere her husband had allegedly put
OL,8,Fhis tongue in A's mouth, she said:
OL,9,F"Ugh, no."
OL,11,FAsked about the allegations made by
OL,12,Fboth complainants, Eleanor Donaldson
OL,13,Fsaid: "This is a massive, massive
OL,14,Fshock."
OL,16,FEarlier, the jury had heard a
OL,17,Frecording of Jeffrey Donaldson's final
OL,18,Finterview with police in 2024.
