OL,3,CLady Donaldson tells trial of 'blank
OL,4,Cwall' from husband over incident
OL,6,FHe added: "I stand over everything I
OL,7,Fsaid in that letter and nowhere in
OL,8,Fthat letter did I indicate nor was I
OL,9,Falluding to incidents of sexual abuse."
OL,11,FAsked if he believed the two
OL,12,Fcomplainants are lying, Donaldson
OL,13,Fsaid: "I'm saying that the specific
OL,14,Fallegations that have been put to me
OL,15,Fare untrue."
OL,17,FA police officer asked him: "Do you
OL,18,Ffeel you've had a fair opportunity to
OL,19,Fgive your account?"
OL,21,FHe said: "Yeah, yes."
